 which makes the leaves turn slightly 

00:00:21.180 --> 00:00:24.180
 We will begin to look at his tree, facing him 

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:31.480
 and we will try to determine all the stems that have grown and that we will be able to eliminate. 

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:36.320
 We start working the tree on the low branches, and we go back slowly, 

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:39.940
 which will allow to work gradually, 

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:41.940
 and go back on his tree while still working on the scale. 

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:46.580
 What we will try to do is produce fine branching 

