 This tree has a dominant apical, 

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:34.500
 he tends to push up. 

00:02:34.500 --> 00:02:37.460
 So you have several possibilities each time, 

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:42.200
 many choices, and the goal is still to leave him his natural port. 

